Process called "dockerfile_semantic_analyze" takes dockerfile_ast as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Perform semantic analysis on Dockerfile AST

    Let analyzer be proc create_dockerfile_semantic_analyzer
    If analyzer is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If

    Let result be proc analyze_dockerfile from analyzer, dockerfile_ast
    Return analyzer
End Process

Process called "dockerfile_semantic_get_errors" takes analyzer as Integer returns Integer:
